  <num>42-3671.08</num>
  <heading>Receipts and accounts.</heading>
  <text>A lessor shall provide to the consumer a written receipt for each payment made by cash or money order.</text>
  <annotations>
    <annotation doc="D.C. Law 14-99" type="History" path="§9">Apr. 13, 2002, D.C. Law 14-99, § 9, 49 DCR 1000</annotation>
